    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a practical option for anyone needing a dependable mode of transportation on a budget. The exterior has several visible scuffs and a few small dents, and the interior shows clear signs of use, including some wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or tires. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that isn't perfect but still has plenty of life left in it.",
