      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving Bavarian engineering, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory limited-slip differential. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS overhaul with Beisan systems, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe with Turner plates to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains precise with zero bushing play, and the factory Laguna Seca Blue paint maintains its original luster. Mechanically flawless and free of any vacuum leaks or VANOS rattle, this chassis represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance.",
